details.name: Extinction
details.description: Finish your journey through the worlds of ARK in ‘Extinction’, where the story began and ends: on Earth itself! An Element-infested, ravaged planet filled with fantastical creatures both organic & technological, Earth holds both the secrets of the past and the keys to its salvation. As a veteran Survivor who has conquered all previous obstacles, your ultimate challenge awaits: can you defeat the gigantic roaming Titans which dominate the planet, and complete the ARK cycle to save Earth's future?

engrams.name: Cannon Shell
engrams.description: A large artillery shell. Used as ammunition for the Mek Siege Cannon Module.

engrams.name: Cryofridge
engrams.description: Requires electricity to run. Keeps Cryopods alive forever!

engrams.name: Delivery Crate
engrams.description: A box with a Gasbag attached that can be used to deliver items to another location.

engrams.name: Dino Leash
engrams.description: Electronic leash to keep your dinos from wandering too far.

engrams.name: Empty Cryopod
engrams.description: Hold up to a creature to capture it. Throw to deploy a captured creature.

engrams.name: Gacha Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Gacha with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Gasbags Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Gasbags with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Large Taxidermy Base
engrams.description: Place a harvested dermis to show off your prowess!

engrams.name: M.D.S.M.
engrams.description: Mek Deployable Shield Module. Equip a Mek with this module to arm it with a large deployable dome shield. Unequipping reduces durability.

engrams.name: M.O.M.I.
engrams.description: MegaMek Operational Materialization Interface. Drag this to a Mek Module slot to enable forming the MegaMek! Requires three additional nearby Meks to transform. Will fail to operate unless in range of the Alpha King Titan.

engrams.name: M.R.L.M.
engrams.description: Mek Rocket Launcher Module. Equip a Mek with this module to arm it with a wide reaching swarm-fire rocket launcher. Unequipping reduces durability. Requires Rocket Pods to fire.

engrams.name: M.S.C.M.
engrams.description: Mek Siege Cannon Module. Equip a Mek with this module to arm it with a powerful long-range siege cannon. Unequipping reduces durability. Requires Cannon Shells to fire.
